1.General Shortcuts
SNO	SHORTCUTKEY	DESCRIPTION
1	Ctrl+N                        	           New Query Window for Current Database
2	Ctrl+O                        	           Open Saved .sql File
3	Ctrl+S            	           Save Current Query Window
4	Ctrl+Shift+S            	           Save All Documents
5	Ctrl+P            	           Print
6	Ctrl+z            	           Undo
7	Ctrl+Y            	           Redo
8	Ctrl+x            	           Cut
9	Ctrl+C            	           Copy
10	Ctrl+V	           Paste
11	Ctrl+A	           Select All
12	Ctrl+tab	           Toggle between opened tabs
2.Find and Replace
SNO	SHORTCUTKEY	DESCRIPTION
13	Ctrl+G                        	           Go To specified Line Number
14	Ctrl+F                        	           Find Word in Current/Entire All Opened Documents
15	Ctrl+H                        	           Replace
3.Text Formatting
SNO	SHORTCUTKEY	DESCRIPTION
16	Ctrl+Shift+U            	           Convert Uppercase for Selected Text
17	Ctrl+Shift+L            	           Convert Lowercase for Selected Text
18	Ctrl+k and Ctrl+\            	           Delete Horizontal White Space at the end of the Word
19	Ctrl+k and Ctrl+C            	           Comment Current Line
20	Ctrl+k and Ctrl+U            	           Uncomment current Line
21	Ctrl+Alt+Space            	           Context Help
22	Alt+RightArrow            	           Complete Current Word
23	Crl+K and Crl+x            	           Insert Code Snippet
24	Ctrl+k and Ctrl+S            	           Surround With Code Snippet
4.Sql server management studio window shortcut keys
SNO	SHORTCUTKEY	DESCRIPTION
25	Ctrl+Alt+L            	           Show Solution Explorer
26	Ctrl+Alt+T            	           Show Template Explorer
27	Ctrl+Alt+o            	           Show Output Window
28	Ctrl+Alt+K            	           Open Task List
29	Ctrl+Alt+X            	           Open Toolbox
30	Ctrl+Alt+R            	           Open Web browser in Sql server
31	F8            	           Object Explorer
32	F7            	           Object Explorer Details
33	Alt+Shift+Enter            	           Toggle Full Screen on and off
34	Ctrl+\ and Ctrl+E	           Show Error List
35	Ctrl+K and Ctrl+B	           Open Code Snippets Manager
36	Ctrl+K and Ctrl+W	           open Bookmark Window
5.Query Shortcut Keys
SNO	SHORTCUTKEY	DESCRIPTION
37	F5            	           Execute Query
38	Ctrl+E            	           Execute Query
39	Alt+X            	           Execute Query
40	Alt+break            	           Stop Current Executing query
41	Alt+ScrollLock            	           Stop Current Executing Query
42	Ctrl+F5            	           Execute Query Without running Results(Parse)
43	Ctrl+L            	           Display Estimated Execution Plan
44	Ctrl+M                        	           Display Actual Execution Plan
45	Ctrl+Shift+Q            	           Construct Query in Design Window
46	Ctrl+Alt+P	           Trace Query in sql profiler
6.Query output Shortcut keys
SNO	SHORTCUTKEY	DESCRIPTION
47	Ctrl+T                        	           Display Query Output in Text
48	Ctrl+D            	           Display Query Output in Grid
49	Ctrl+Shift+F                        	           Save Query output in File with .rpt Extension
50	Ctrl+R            	           Toggle Result Window show or hide
